Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say rearguards are\Nthe true heroes of the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the castle, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll leave them to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Let's go inside the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the rooftop, the battle between the Minks and Jack\Ncontinued in front of Kaido.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To stop Jack's rampage,\NDogstorm and Cat Viper finally turned into Sulongs, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Queen let loose a new version of the Plague Rounds\Naimed at Zoro and Drake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this bullet is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Heroic Blade!\NAkazaya vs. Kaido, Again Once More!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I've finally made it this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ogres!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally used...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Plague Rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this all about?!\NWhat's in those bullets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so curious, get shot!\NAs soon as that happens, you'll know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear son! Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks so desperate...\NWhy can't we just listen to what he has to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy said he's our ally...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0},\Nwe're in the enemy's stronghold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't trust someone\Nwho identifies himself as Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can't we just listen to him...\N--Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}! Don't fall for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...want to talk to my father again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! I'll go all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took all I've got to take him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slice through you with all my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Lead Performers of\Nthe Animal Kingdom Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack the Drought!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the resentment and bitterness from the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle it once and for all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duke-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should let us settle the score with him-{\i1}meow{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He-{\i1}gara{\i0} is truly like a disaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Minks will never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The awful poisonous-gas-filled vision\Nis burned in all Minks' memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how many people writhed in agony\Nand gave way to despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I saw you-{\i1}gara{\i0} earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my severed left arm has been tingling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This leg that you-{\i1}gara{\i0} cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is itching...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to chop you up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn little Minks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be completely destroyed this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone go up!\NDon't let them get in Luffy and the others' way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanda! No matter how many of them we cut,\Nthey keep coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get run down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop! Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep running like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me! Let's stop them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Wanda. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to check something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got thrown this far outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They caught me off-guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Perospero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, Mama! I need to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you came at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to see you here, Marco.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Whitebeard's group already fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have the same objective as your son...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogre extermination-{\i1}yoi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to bring down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We teamed up for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, the alliance that everyone's talking about\Nreally was formed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you heard about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We formed a pirate alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding, Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't ally with Kaido!\NHe's not trustworthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perospero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you second-guessing my decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get the One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack is one of our Lead Performers that I handpicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for me to keep quiet\Nas my precious subordinate is beaten to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're not weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the Sulongs,\Nwe sustained serious damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you did a good job\Ncornering those Sulongs as much as you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get yourself treated.\NYou've already done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:50.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,INSIDE THE CASTLE\NBANQUET HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island is in tumult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are they gonna come up here?\N--I can't believe no one's here in the banquet hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Maria, will you sing us a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the snowy night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two who missed each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But they didn't get a chance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To see each other for so long{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally seeing each other!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Under the moonlight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That excitement!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Perospero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to form an alliance with Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we family members have always wanted\NMama to become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you guys trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I'm relieved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we don't share the mutual objective of\Nogre extermination anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perospero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accepted your offer but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco! I can't believe you helped those punks.\NI thought you were better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the remnants of Whitebeard's group\Ndon't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you misunderstanding\Nthe meaning of the word "remnant"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think Pops' voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...still binds us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We who were left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are free-{\i1}yoi{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the dead can't speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm free to do whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...had a feeling that this would be my last journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Pedro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, you'll see how important it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to save Luffy and the others here\Nand let them set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You-{\i1}gara{\i0} guys must go forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found Pedro's foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}san{\i0}! Go ahead now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Straw Hat and Black-Leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll eventually\Nget tired from running and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see how many you can dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxfire Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame-Rend!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought we were gonna run?\NThat's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sick of running!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick of hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us die as Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutching your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After keeping their passionate, ground-shaking\Nhearts beating for years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with their love for their lord Oden,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Akazaya members come together\Nto save the Land of Wano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forged blades! Now is the time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The legendary secret arts will finish Kaido!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Inherited Technique! Unleashing Oden's Secret Swordplay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
